INSERT INTO `reviews` VALUES (4,'I bought this for my 2yo to use on long road trips. One of the things I really like about it is that it hooks on to the headrest posts rather than onto the cushion part, which means that it can be used simultaneously with a mirror for her rear facing car seat! We’ve used it for a couple of trips now and it has worked out great. I think the angle would be better if it was used on the back of a seat for a front facing passenger, but it still worked out well enough. It would be nice if the angle was a bit more adjustable than it is. We have an Amazon kids tab and this won’t work with the case on. It isn’t a huge deal yet that we have to take it out because she can’t really reach it to take it out yet, but I can see that being a problem in the future once she can reach. Also, the tablet only fits in horizontally and cannot be used vertically. If you use a cell phone though, that could be (at least mine can. I suppose it depends on how tall your phone is).\r\n','Pretty Good!',4,'2022-11-09 16:59:45.457000',3,5,1),(5,'Very good tablet mount in general. Only issue is full size iPad won’t fit. If you stretch it, you might get it to work assuming no protection sleeves. Personally, I will only use it for iPad mini.','Good mount for smaller tablets',3,'2022-11-09 17:05:42.145000',3,1,1),(6,'I used these 20\'\'20 inserts for 18\'\'18 covers and it worked out great.\r\n\r\nThese will not fluff immediately as soon as they come out of the pack. You will feel disheartened but wait don\'t loose hope and follow the fluffing instructions. You will not regret. they will fluff up magically.\r\n\r\nYou can use the dryer with a tennis ball to fluff them up or you can punch your pillows from all sides and in the middle for some time so that they fluff up. I used both the methods and they fluffed up really well.','Size up to make it look fuller!',4,'2022-11-10 17:07:58.989000',3,16,1);
